Topic: Deep Product Knowledge & Basic Skin Understanding

👀 On the first day of class, we always start with the basics. Before we even begin makeup application, it’s important that our students understand skin — because good makeup starts with good skin knowledge.

👀 This helps in choosing the right products and techniques for each client.

👀 Next, we introduce makeup brushes — because just like a writer needs to know their pen, we, as makeup artists, must know our tools. Brushes are our “kalam” (pen), and it’s essential to understand how to use them properly:
	•	What each brush is used for
	•	How to hold them
	•	How to maintain them
